Explainer

&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/privacysandbox/tpcd-labeling/blob/main/cookie_deprecation_labeling_explainer.md"&gt;https://github.com/privacysandbox/tpcd-labeling/blob/main/cookie_deprecation_labeling_explainer.md&lt;/a&gt; 
&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/privacysandbox/tpcd-labeling/blob/main/cookie_deprecation_labeling_explainer.md"&gt;https://github.com/privacysandbox/tpcd-labeling/blob/main/cookie_deprecation_labeling_explainer.md&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
