7. &lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Permissions_Policy#allowlists"&gt;https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Permissions_Policy#allowlists&lt;/a&gt;
