&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; not requested a signal for this change specifically. The Gecko position 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; on 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Shared Storage (one of the ways Private Aggregation is exposed) is 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; negative.
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
