&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; That’s correct! In isolation, cleartext payloads will be ~5x larger.
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; In terms of magnitude, typical report sizes will increase from ~1.5 KiB
&gt;&gt;&gt; to ~6 KiB. (Double these estimates when debug mode is enabled.)
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; OK, that's not awful.
