in isolated contexts will launch the latest by M132 (I am targeting to make 
the branch date for M131). The only work left is to land a CL that exposes 
the API in isolated contexts while still keeping the OT on the drive-by web 
open. This way, developers have at least 4 milestones to pivot.&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

I will update the Chrome status entry.

