&lt;span class="date"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=date:20240802" rel="nofollow"&gt;Fri, 02 Aug 2024 07:47:22 -0700&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
